The '''Zilveren Harp''' (Silver Harp) is a   given annually to promising al talent. The award is very prestigious and winners are chosen by a different  each year. The Zilveren Harp is given by the  "", which aims to promote Dutch music.
The first award was given in 1969, and it has been presented every year since (except for the year 1972).
